item.description: Date: Thu, 30 Nov 2000 10:12:22 -0600 From: Lizzie Subject: too late. the door code has been changed and the stickers have all been removed from the outside door. it's over. and we've lost. i'm up at the station now and it's not a pretty picture. either we do something now or not at all, but if we do anything it must be coordinated and immediate. 9:58am 30 November 2000
